data.description: BACK ON MARKET AT NO FAULT TO THE SELLERS.Located in the Sunny Hills Golf Course Community, this beautiful, spacious 4 Bedroom, 2 Bathroom Home is calling your name! The split floorpan offers this over 2,000 sqft home room live and entertain! After walking into the foyer, you're greeted by 18x18 tile floors. The formal dining room is to the left, featuring crown molding, chair molding and rain with wainscoting. The family room offers a Heatilator Fireplace, vaulted ceilings, recessed lights, a custom built-in entertainment unit and beautiful French Doors leading to the back patio. The eat in kitchen offers lots of cabinetry plus a pantry! There's a separate bar opening with views of the family room. There is a home generator, a pole barn and a shed with a lean too for room for covered storage. Bring your boats, toys or other recreational vehicles as there is PLENTY of room to store them.  Come experience what Sunny Hills has to offer. With close access to some of North West Floridas best Hunting and Fishing while still being less than 40 miles from the ''Worlds Most Beautiful Beaches''!If important, please verify all information. Call a Realtor today to schedule your private showing!
